{"title":"Spread Your Adventure Wings with the New Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar","link":"https://bikerumor.com/new-ritchey-comp-buzzard-bar-wide-upright/","date":1711378920000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-hero-800x491.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"491\" alt=\"(Photos/Ritchey Comp)\" /></p>\n<p>Helping to spread <em>your</em> wings, the new <a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ritchey</a> Comp <a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/bike/handlebars/comp-buzzard-handlebar\" target=\"_blank\">Buzzard Bar</a> is made for your next adventure. The new Buzzard Bar takes the adventurous spirit of the Ritchey Comp <a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/bike/handlebars/comp-kyote-handlebar\" target=\"_blank\">Kyote Bar</a> and takes it up a few notches. The Buzzard is designed for true all-day, off-road touring and bikepacking. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s check out some of the comfortable and practical features of the Buzzard. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"784\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar cockpit closeup\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup-297x182.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup-800x490.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup-120x74.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-cockpit-closeup-768x470.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Ritchey Comp)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Right out of the gate the Buzzard rises above similar adventure bars with a 70mm flat rise. This leads to a more upright, and comfy riding position, perfect for touring or bikepacking. The 70mm rise would be especially helpful on bikes with lower stack height. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar singletrackin\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin-297x193.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin-800x519.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin-120x78.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-singletrackin-768x498.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The modest reach of the Buzzard along with the rise means that there will be minimal pressure on the wrists, allowing the rider to settle back in a less aggressive, more sustainable riding position.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar charge the hill\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-charge-the-hill-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Complementing the Buzzard Bar’s comfort are the practical features that are built into the bar’s geometry. First, the bar’s ample width of 820mm ensures plenty of control, when the ride gets rough. Second, pair that with the aforementioned rise, and you get a better line of sight to help see what’s next. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar relaxed corner\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-relaxed-corner-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Third, the Buzzard Bar’s wide center section allows the attachment of all kinds of bags and accessories for those lengthy adventures. And finally, top all of that goodness with a low price, and you get a bar that is attainable and ready for whatever you throw at it. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Buzzard Bar’s Purpose</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar upright and comfy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-upright-and-comfy-768x576.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>The true calling of the Buzzard is to seek rides that float over woodland, deserts, mountains, or anywhere you want to escape to with ease and grace – be it joyfully meandering endless trails all day or tackling that 1000-kilometer bikepacking event you’ve been contemplating</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>The Buzzard isn’t a bar for wannabees – it’s a bar for where-do-you-wannabe?”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Buzzard’s Retail and Specs</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"664\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing.jpeg\" alt=\"Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar drawing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing-297x154.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing-800x415.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing-120x62.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Ritchey-Comp-Buzzard-Bar-drawing-768x398.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $49.95</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Specifications</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Material: double-butted 6061 alloy</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Width: 820mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rise: 70mm flat rise</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Backsweep: 27.5°</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Clamp diameter: 31.8mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bar-end compatible: yes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight: 367g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Color: BB black</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out more at the link below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RitcheyLogic.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-ritchey-comp-buzzard-bar-wide-upright/\">Spread Your Adventure Wings with the New Ritchey Comp Buzzard Bar</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"033d121b5de060b83b52afa4110587a8e2959e1c081f38a0ee9a3ea332904004","category":"Cycling"}